        <p>For example, for the trail <italic>t</italic>=(<italic>r</italic><sub>6</sub>, <italic>r</italic><sub>2</sub>, <italic>r</italic><sub>3</sub>, <italic>r</italic><sub>7</sub>, <italic>r</italic><sub>8</sub>) in Fig. <xref rid="Fig1" ref-type="fig">1</xref>b and the gene neighborhood in Fig. <xref rid="Sec9" ref-type="sec">2</xref> for the reference species <italic>S</italic> and another species <italic>S</italic><sub>1</sub>, <inline-formula id="IEq92"><alternatives><tex-math id="M183">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
